      <h2>Understanding Joint and Muscular Pain</h2>
      <p>Joint and muscular pain can significantly affect one's quality of life, limiting mobility and causing discomfort. Understanding the causes and treatment options for these types of pain is crucial for managing symptoms and improving overall well-being.</p>
      <p>Joint pain is often associated with conditions such as arthritis, while muscular pain can result from overuse, injury, or underlying medical conditions. This guide explores the common causes, symptoms, and effective strategies for managing joint and muscular pain.</p>
